Roles & Responsibilities
Job Summary
We are looking for a Data Analyst who can leverage his/her analytics skills to support various business units and work closely with key stakeholders to drive data analytics initiatives.

Mandatory Skill-set
Degree holder majoring in Business, Finance, Computer Science or equivalent;
At least 5 years of hands on experience in Tableau, Qlik or Power BI;
Strong in developing data pipeline and working on statistical modelling;
Working knowledge in Cloud platform such as AWS, Azure, Cloudera;
Familiar with SQL, scripting, programming languages (Python, R, Java);
Experience using analytical software (SPSS, SAS) and distributed architectures systems (HDFS, Hive, Spark);
Team player, self motivated and resourceful;
Numerically inclined with a strong analytical mind.
Desired Skill-set
Experience in Cloud / Big Data.
Responsibilities
Responsible for identifying business problems and developing analytical solutions;
Create data pipelines and data lake through tools such as SQL, NoSQL;
Extract reports from multiple sources, transform raw data into actionable items;
Design dashboards and automated reports using visualization tools such as Tableau, Qlik or Power BI;
Identify accurate data sources and data features to assist in the development of data science algorithms;
Simplify complex data concepts and present it to non-technical audiences;
Responsible for planning, execution and to oversee operations of data analytics to ensure quality;
Work together with key stakeholders to provide data reporting and drive business objectives;
Continuously learning about the industry trends.

Should you be interested in this career opportunity, please send in your updated resume to apply@sciente.com at the earliest.

When you apply, you voluntarily consent to the disclosure, collection and use of your personal data for employment/recruitment and related purposes in accordance with the SCIENTE Group Privacy Policy, a copy of which is published at SCIENTE’s website (https://www.sciente.com/privacy-policy).

Confidentiality is assured, and only shortlisted candidates will be notified for interviews.

